author: David O'Shaughnessy
title: WTF | Watch: Let this dog repeatedly jumping into a pile of leaves give you that Friday feeling
text:
Autumn when it's wet is the most miserable and soggy of occasions, but when it's dry it's a crunchy, leafy paradise.
Stella here knows what's up, and repeatedly dives and runs straight into the most inviting pile of leaves you'll ever see and wish you had for yourself. We'd lie if we said we weren't jealous.
Via YouTube
